4. Copy templates and static files
   ```bash
   # Copy all templates
   cp -r /home/mlk/flaskrag3/templates/* /home/mlk/smartlib/templates/
   
   # Copy static files
   cp -r /home/mlk/flaskrag3/static/* /home/mlk/smartlib/static/
   ```

5. Set up database migrations
   ```bash
   # If migrations exist, copy them with the same directory structure
   if [ -d "/home/mlk/flaskrag3/migrations" ]; then
     echo "Copying existing migrations..."
     cp -r /home/mlk/flaskrag3/migrations/* /home/mlk/smartlib/migrations/
     
     # Copy alembic.ini if it exists
     if [ -f "/home/mlk/flaskrag3/alembic.ini" ]; then
       cp /home/mlk/flaskrag3/alembic.ini /home/mlk/smartlib/
     fi
   else
     # Initialize fresh migrations if none exist
     echo "Initializing fresh migrations..."
     cd /home/mlk/smartlib
     export FLASK_APP=app.py
     flask db init
     
     # If database already exists with schema, create a first migration
     if [ -f "/home/mlk/smartlib/data/app.db" ]; then
       flask db migrate -m "Initial migration"
       flask db stamp head
     fi
   fi
   ```
   
   > **NOTE**: If no migrations folder exists in the original project, we'll initialize fresh migrations. If you have an existing database with schema, the migration will be created based on the current schema.

6. Copy toolkits and scripts
   ```bash
   # Copy all toolkits
   cp -r /home/mlk/flaskrag3/toolkits/* /home/mlk/smartlib/toolkits/
   
   # Copy essential scripts
   cp /home/mlk/flaskrag3/scripts/* /home/mlk/smartlib/scripts/
   ```

7. Copy ARM templates
   ```bash
   # Copy the production-ready template
   cp /home/mlk/flaskrag3/ARMtemplate/flask_appservice_template_shared_plan.json /home/mlk/smartlib/ARMtemplate/
   cp /home/mlk/flaskrag3/ARMtemplate/flask_appservice_template_conditional_kv.json /home/mlk/smartlib/ARMtemplate/
   cp /home/mlk/flaskrag3/ARMtemplate/celery_worker_appservice.json /home/mlk/smartlib/ARMtemplate/
   
   # Copy ARM template documentation
   cp /home/mlk/flaskrag3/ARMtemplate/docs/QUICK_START_GUIDE.md /home/mlk/smartlib/ARMtemplate/docs/
   cp /home/mlk/flaskrag3/ARMtemplate/docs/SHARED_PLAN_GUIDE.md /home/mlk/smartlib/ARMtemplate/docs/
   ```

